Sunday 29.7.17
Flooded out from our improvised shelter by a very heavy storm. Last of the 6th Bgde left to-day. All enthusiasm regarding the move died out, just taken as a matter of course.
Monday 30.7.17
Our Brigade on the move C Section of our unit left at 4 pm, still remained on guard. Entrained at midnight with the remainder of the boys; travelled the distance in an open goods truck with the goods we were guarding; very cold wet.
Tuesday 31.7.17
